## 1. Architecture Overview

This integration implements the **Librarian-Navigator pattern** from the `install_on_Alpha.md` specification:

- **Open Notebook (ON)** acts as the **Librarian** — a persistent semantic index of the codebase
- **Opencode (OC)** acts as the **Navigator** — querying the librarian to find and navigate code
- **35B Model** (Qwen3.6-35B-A3B-Q4_K_M) handles heavy indexing and analysis
- **7B Model** (Qwen3.5-9B, optional) handles lightweight routing and query processing

### Two-Tier Compression Pipeline

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    Opencode (OC) Navigator                   │
│              - Routing queries via structured grammar          │
│              - Small model (7B) or direct API calls          │
└────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────┘
                         │ HTTP POST /query
┌────────────────────────▼──────────────────────────────────────┐
│              Open Notebook Librarian (Port 8081)              │
│              - FastAPI server with semantic index              │
│              - Sub-millisecond response times                │
├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  MASTER_RECON_PHONEBOOK.md  — 291 modules, 10 layers (Open Notebook)│
│  DEPENDENCY_GRAPH.json      — 97 cross-layer edges (Open Notebook)     │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                         │ Generation Pipeline (as needed)
┌────────────────────────▼──────────────────────────────────────┐
│              35B Model Server (Port 8080)                      │
│              Qwen_Qwen3.6-35B-A3B-Q4_K_M.gguf                │
│              - Heavy indexing and analysis                     │
│              - 4.4GB VRAM active, 14GB system RAM             │
│              - ~12 t/s generation, ~7 t/s prompt processing   │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

