## 6. Operational Procedures

### 6.1 After Code Changes

When the codebase changes, regenerate the phonebook:

```bash
cd /home/nos/labware/open-notebook

# Step 1: Regenerate artifacts
python3 scripts/pipeline/generate_phonebook.py /home/nos/labware/open-notebook

# Step 2: Reload librarian index
curl -X POST http://localhost:8081/reload

# Step 3: Verify
python3 scripts/pipeline/check_integration.py
```

### 6.2 Monitoring

Check all service health:
```bash
# Open Notebook
curl -s http://localhost:5055/health

# 35B Model Server
curl -s http://localhost:8080/v1/models

# Librarian
curl -s http://localhost:8081/health
```

### 6.3 Troubleshooting

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| Librarian returns empty results | Run `curl -X POST http://localhost:8081/reload` |
| Phonebook out of date | Regenerate with `generate_phonebook.py` |
| 35B server OOM | Reduce `--ctx-size` or use `--no-mmap` |
| Docker containers down | `docker compose up -d` |
| Model server not responding | Check `ps aux \| grep llama-server` |

